Tollanar.creatorRace: Aearee (known as avians, and creators of the aarakocra, kenku, and other birdlike humanoids)

Aduria.creatorRace: Batrachi (creators of the bullywugs, doppelgangers, kopru, kuo-toa, locathah, sivs, tako and other shapeshifting, amphibious, or piscine races)

Djapar.creatorRace: Sarrukh (creators of the yuan-ti, naga, lizardfolk, and scalykind)
